006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.ObjectUtils;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012/**
013 * A base class for an assembly instance defined inline.
014 *
015 * @param <PARENT>
016 *          the Java type of the parent model container for this instance
017 * @param <DEFINITION>
018 *          the Java type of the related assembly definition
019 * @param <INSTANCE>
020 *          the expected Java type of an instance of this definition
021 * @param <PARENT_DEFINITION>
022 *          the Java type of the containing assembly definition
023 * @param <FLAG>
024 *          the expected Java type of flag children
025 * @param <MODEL>
026 *          the expected Java type of model children
027 * @param <NAMED_MODEL>
028 *          the expected Java type of named model children
029 * @param <FIELD>
030 *          the expected Java type of field children
031 * @param <ASSEMBLY>
032 *          the expected Java type of assembly children
033 * @param <CHOICE>
034 *          the expected Java type of choice children
035 * @param <CHOICE_GROUP>
036 *          the expected Java type of choice group children
037 */
038public abstract class AbstractInlineAssemblyDefinition<
039    PARENT extends IContainerModel,
040    DEFINITION extends IAssemblyDefinition,
041    INSTANCE extends IAssemblyInstance,
042    PARENT_DEFINITION extends IAssemblyDefinition,
043    FLAG extends IFlagInstance,
044    MODEL extends IModelInstanceAbsolute,
045    NAMED_MODEL extends INamedModelInstanceAbsolute,
046    FIELD extends IFieldInstanceAbsolute,
047    ASSEMBLY extends IAssemblyInstanceAbsolute,
048    CHOICE extends IChoiceInstance,
049    CHOICE_GROUP extends IChoiceGroupInstance>
050    extends AbstractNamedModelInstance<PARENT, PARENT_DEFINITION>
051    implements IAssemblyInstance, IAssemblyDefinition, IFeatureContainerFlag<FLAG>,
052    IFeatureContainerModelAssembly<
053        MODEL,
054        NAMED_MODEL,
055        FIELD,
056        ASSEMBLY,
057        CHOICE,
058        CHOICE_GROUP>,
059    IFeatureDefinitionInstanceInlined<DEFINITION, INSTANCE> {
060
061  /**
062   * Construct a new inline assembly definition.
063   *
064   * @param parent
065   *          the parent model containing this instance
066   */
067  protected AbstractInlineAssemblyDefinition(@NonNull PARENT parent) {
068    super(parent);
069  }
070
071  @Override
072  public final DEFINITION getDefinition() {
073    return ObjectUtils.asType(this);
074  }
075
076  @Override
077  public boolean isInline() {
078    return true;
079  }
080
081  @Override
082  @NonNull
083  public final INSTANCE getInlineInstance() {
084    return ObjectUtils.asType(this);
085  }
086
087  @Override
088  public final FLAG getJsonKey() {
089    return IFeatureContainerFlag.super.getJsonKey();
090  }
091}
